ganga/python/GangaAtlas
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Athena:
* Fix bug #42661: User packages not being recognised in Athena Root dir
* Fix bug #43946, DQ2_COPY mode for multiple datasets should work now 
  properly again. (AthenaLCGRTHandlerpy, AthenaLocalRTHandler.py)
* Fix bug #44213: input.txt is now created in DQ2_COPY mode for ARA 
* Fix bug #43702: if no files to stage-out, job should be marked as failed 
* Add new version of libdcap.so to fix read ahead buffer problems
* Make DCACHE_RA_BUFFER configurable - 
  Default is config['Athena']['DCACHE_RA_BUFFER'] = 32768
* Add Athena.stats: collects statistics after job finish 
  from logfiles for the LCG backend - not correct for DQ2_COPY mode
* run-athena-lcg.sh: Improve fail-over mechanisms for DQ2_COPY mode,
  check file download, more retries, add debug mode
* Fix bug
* DQ2JobSplitter: spitting in subjobs now correctly only per single dataset
* DQ2JobSplitter.update_siteindex=True/False: switch for file
  location update call during job submission
* Add warning message for failed submission in dataset splitting 
  mode (AthenaLCGRTHandler.py)

AthenaMC:
* AthenaMCLCGRTHandler.py: Fixing condition trigger false warning 
  in input data splitting
* Updating default output storage location to CERN-PROD_USERDISK 
  as CERNCAF is long obsolete. Relaxing constraint on job matching 
  to let jobs running at CERN as CERN Tier 2 facility is not 
  properly tagged in LCG BDII
* AthenaMCDatasets: adding exception handling of incomplete records 
  of input datasets in the DQ2 database (datasets with no known locations)
* AthenaMC: 
  - Change defvalue of partition_number
  - Bug fix for inputdata.inputfiles type, improving timeout evaluation 
    for stage-out, allowing support for stage-in files from SRMV2 space 
    tokens, extending splitter to allow partial resubmission of master 
    jobs (all failed subjobs at once instead of one by one.)

AMAAthena:
* introduce the exit code in the athena_setup routine and stop 
  the main wrapper when the exit code returned is not 0

tests:
* Updated AthenaMC.gpi input datasets. The previously used datasets 
  have been removed from DQ2 database, causing the tests to crash


